The '''NightWhispers''' were an elite [[Storm commando/Legends|storm commando]] unit of at least platoon size which served under the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]]. The NightWhispers were often used for missions which required stealth in order to gain access to the enemy. As a veteran unit, NightWhisper commandos were more skilled than most Storm Commando units and had access to heavy supporting firepower. During a search for a crashed Rebel operative on NCW-781, the NightWhispers were supported by a [[Strike-class medium cruiser]], [[TIE/sa tactical bomber/Legends|TIE/sa bombers]], [[CompForce/Legends|CompForce]] assault troops, and a [[HAVr A9 Floating Fortress/Legends|HAVr A9 Floating Fortress]]; in addition they were able to call in the [[Imperial-class Star Destroyer/Legends|Imperial-class Star Destroyer]] [[Rampage (Imperial-class)|''Rampage'']] to interdict a fleeing [[Alliance Special Forces/Legends|Alliance Special Forces]] rescue team. The NightWhispers were seen operating closely with the [[Shadow stormtrooper/Legends|Shadow stormtrooper]] units of [[Cronal]].

